PLEASE READ: So YouTube is on the rampage. Last week I learned that YouTube is redefining their rules. Tons of channels are getting multiple strikes.

They're receiving strikes for the following:

1.Inserting mags of 30 rounds or More. The algorithm is now counting how many rounds are fired from a mag. 

2.Threading on suppressors or other muzzle attachments.

3. Actively attaching anything in the video such as lights, lasers, red dots, Scopes etc. 

I haven't uploaded in a while, because I've been re-editing my video library. And I want to do my best to have everything fixed before  uploading another video. 

If you want to support your favorite guntubers make sure that your subscribed to their channels and have notifications turned on. Because there's power in numbers.

For the record, pretty much all of us are already backed up on Rumble, odysee etc.

The real problem is, If Rumble or any other platform becomes real competition for YouTube, Google will simply buy that platform out. Then we're in the same boat again.

I just found out that YouTube deleted @kit_badger Channel due to YouTube redifining their Guidelines. The fastest way to get this overturned is for 1000's of us to go to Twitter and create a Tweet demanding that YouTube restore his channel. Make sure to include @ TeamYouTube in your tweet.

I'm not buying it... Think about it, they can already spy on everyone and everything with cell phones, smart watches, ring cameras, GPS in cars, air tags, and with satellites that are in low earth orbit. Why would they need a balloon? What information could this balloon collect that they don't already have access to through other means? 

How do we as Americans know with certainty that these balloons actually came from the far east? How do we know that they didn't come from our own people as a way to justify war? Remember the Lusitania?
We already know that the mainstream media lies, why should we trust the narrative this time?
I could be completely wrong, but I'd love to hear your thoughts..

I could be wrong, but I think a planned fake invasion is coming soon...

In the mid 90's when I was 11. One of my dad's friends told me all of this was going to happen, including the big thing that happened in 2001.

He went into detail about how it's a systematic approach to lower the population and strip the remaining people of their rights.

At the time it scared the crap out of me. But he told me not to be afraid because the majority of it was smoke and mirrors intended to scare people into submission. 

He mentioned one of the final steps was a Fake Invasion from outer space. With the goal being to unite the world against a common enemy. Thus making the population easier to control.

So far he's been pretty much spot on...unfortunately he passed away 12 years ago, so I can't ask him anymore questions.

What's your thoughts?

What's Your Thoughts on the PSA Sabre? For under $1k you get - Billet or Forged Receivers

- 4 stock and grip choices Including B5 Systems

-4 handguard choices including  Geissele

- 3 Barrel Choices including FN CHF, and 13.7",13.9",and 14.5"

- 2 different BCG Choices, 1 lightweight or Chrome Lined standard weight. 

-Dozens of Muzzle device choices with QD for KeyMo, SureFire, AAC, and Huxworx

- Radian Ambi Charging Handle

- Radian Ambi Safety

- Hiperfire Single Stage Trigger w/JP Springs 3.5lb pull

- Fixed or Adjustable Gas Block Choices, including Geissele Cross Pinned Block.

Note: The Geissele Option cost a little more than 1k, but includes FN CHF Barrel, Geissele handguard and Cross Pinned Geissele Gas Block.
